{"tid":141140,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺 世界真細小 嘅詞其實寫得幾好 (2)","createTime":"2017-03-02T16:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T16:17:00.000Z","uid":10876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b13270ca939e87f8aef3192ce3f47bd9d8ebacf1","tid":141140,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺 世界真細小 嘅詞其實寫得幾好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/138332/page/40?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/138332/page/40?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<blockquote>係街撞到ex <br />\n唔係憎佢 亦唔係仲鍾意<br />\n只不過唔想衰畀佢睇<br />\n<br />\n唔係要佢後悔 妒忌 <br />\n而係唔想畀佢覺得你退步<br />\n唔想畀佢感覺好彩同你分咗手<br />\n有冇人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n李克勤 <br />\n<br />\n世界真細小(&amp; 容祖兒)<br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃偉文<br />\n作曲：C.Y. Kong、Jean Chien<br />\n<br />\n為何上天選今日 沒防備的這一日<br />\n共前度分開多久 偏碰見於這日<br />\n<br />\n沒攜著妻子一日 沒乘坐跑車一日<br />\n如何能給你印象 成就大過昨日<br />\n<br />\n想過早晚會會合 不過此際變事實<br />\n都會驚慌失惜 似行刑受罰<br />\n<br />\n擁抱可會太兀突 (當我傷勢已癒合)<br />\n感覺可似過份 (跟你團聚)<br />\n回味舊愛侶 舊時秘密 (難道談論舊過失)<br />\n<br />\n近來愉快吧 平平無奇沒變化吧<br />\n近來幸福吧 長期情人亦有個吧<br />\n宇宙那麼細 如何迴避亦碰到嗎<br />\n偶遇太可怕<br />\n今天想偶遇嗎 (只好倉促扮優雅)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"38e79167c7abc308eac835a64f381fa99d1ba916","tid":141140,"uid":74285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"x1002"},{"pid":"d099735e1c254a1982f04d8a26963ade98aebfa2","tid":141140,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:38:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>x1002</blockquote><br />\nx1003"},{"pid":"3ab08e5b597a0cde1c0c14a4fe04cc832f903ee8","tid":141140,"uid":4709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>x1002</blockquote><br />\nx1003</blockquote><br />\nX1004<br />\n<br />\nBtw咁既post都可以爆1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/